Im quoting the actions of RITO here;

But intentionally feeding is ok because they're the most skilled players. People who want to climb are the scourge of the game and want them to leave. 

It makes absolutely no sense to me but I feel you. Played 10 hours today and in all that, only 1 team that wasnt all hardcore feeders. Why should we be punished for this level of degenerate behaviour?
